	<div class="inner_content clearfix aflsp_faq">
		<div class="inner_page_title">
			FAQ		</div>
		<div class="left_content left">
<div class="aflsp_faq_accordian">
<ul>
<li class="aflsp_faq_accordian-slide ABCAccordionOpen">
<div class="head clearfix qna">
<div class="question_no left">1.</div>
<div class="question remain">What costs does an Asian Future Leaders Scholarship Program scholarship (the &ldquo;AFLSP Scholarship&rdquo;) cover?</div>
<div class="button"></div>
</div>
<div class="detail qna">
<div class="detail_content">
<p>Subject to a maximum commitment of US$50,000 from Bai Xian Asia Institute, the AFLSP Scholarship is a full scholarship that covers:</p>
<ul class="list">
<li>university tuition fees</li>
<li>university matriculation and other fees</li>
<li>accommodation fee</li>
<li>personal stipend</li>
<li></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="university_content" style="text-align: justify;">Full cost of attending the BXAI Summer Program (accommodation, food, round-trip economy class airfare) will be separately covered.</div>
<div class="university_content" style="text-align: justify;">Financial need is not a consideration in granting the AFLSP Scholarship.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="aflsp_faq_accordian-slide">
<div class="head clearfix qna">
<div class="question_no left">2.</div>
<div class="question remain">Am I allowed to accept other awards in conjunction with an AFLSP Scholarship?</div>
<div class="button"></div>
</div>
<div class="detail qna">
<div class="detail_content" style="text-align: justify;">Bai Xian Asian Scholars must not be a recipient of any other scholarship or any other form of funding from a third party without prior consultation with and consent from Bai Xian Asia Institute.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="aflsp_faq_accordian-slide">
<div class="head clearfix qna">
<div class="question_no left">3.</div>
<div class="question remain">Which field of studies can an AFLSP Scholarship be used for?</div>
<div class="button"></div>
</div>
<div class="detail qna">
<div class="detail_content" style="text-align: justify;">Bai Xian Asian Scholars come from many different academic backgrounds and pursue a wide range of degree programs at our Anchor and Participating Universities. &nbsp;Some universities open the AFLSP to a particular select program only. &nbsp;For details, please review the <span>Unique Program Offerings at each of the&nbsp;</span>Anchor Universities&nbsp;<a   href='/en-us/programs-and-scholarships/universities/anchor-universities/'>here</a>,&nbsp;and refer to the "Participating Universities" page <a href="http://www.bxai.org/en-us/universities/index">here.</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="aflsp_faq_accordian-slide">
<div class="head clearfix qna">
<div class="question_no left">4.</div>
<div class="question remain">How do I apply for the Asian Future Leaders Scholarship Program at a Participating University?</div>
<div class="button"></div>
</div>
<div class="detail qna">
<div class="detail_content" style="text-align: justify;">Please click <a   href='/en-us/programs-and-scholarships/scholarships/selection-criteria'>here</a>&nbsp;for more&nbsp;information on "Eligibility and Selection Criteria"&nbsp;and <a   href='/en-us/programs-and-scholarships/scholarships/application-process-and-timeline'>here</a>&nbsp;for "Application Process and Timeline"; then <a   href='/en-us/programs-and-scholarships/scholarships/apply-now'> APPLY NOW</a>.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="aflsp_faq_accordian-slide">
<div class="head clearfix qna">
<div class="question_no left">5.</div>
<div class="question remain">How do I apply for the Asian Future Leaders Scholarship Program at an Anchor University?</div>
<div class="button"></div>
</div>
<div class="detail qna">
<div class="detail_content" style="text-align: justify;">Each Anchor University operates its own selection process independently for the Asian Future Leaders Scholarship Program ("AFLSP") in compliance with the BXAI Selection Criteria; a recommended list of candidates will be submitted to the Institute for final review and approval.</div>
<div class="detail_content" style="text-align: justify;"><br />Students who wish to apply for the AFLSP at Anchor Universities should review the Unique Program Offerings at each Anchor University <a href="http://www.bxai.org/en-us/programs-and-scholarships/universities">here</a> and apply to the Anchor University directly for admission. The Institute encourages students to contact the relevant university office or program administrator to express their interest.</div>
<div class="university_content">HITOTSUBASHI UNIVERSITY</div>
<div class="detail_content">Administration Office, Graduate School of International Corporate Strategy</div>
<div class="university_detail">
